description: Amundi PEA MSCI USA ESG Selection UCITS ETF - USD seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, whether the trend is rising or falling, the performance of the MSCI USA ESG Selection P-Series 5% Issuer Capped Index (the Index), and to minimize the tracking error between the net asset value of the Sub-Fund and the performance of the Index. The anticipated level of tracking error, under normal market conditions, is indicated in the prospectus of the Sub-Fund. For further information, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi PEA MSCI USA ESG Selection UCITS ETF - USD
